snippet.title: Stephen Colbert Announces The Cancellation Of “The Late Show”
snippet.description:
Stephen Colbert tells his audience that the next season of “The Late Show” will be the last, and that the series will end in May 2026.

#Colbert #Comedy #StephenColbert #TheLateShow

Subscribe To "The Late Show" Channel: http://bit.ly/ColbertYouTube

Watch full episodes of "The Late Show": http://bit.ly/1Puei40
Listen to "The Late Show Pod Show" podcast: https://link.chtbl.com/Awagtx95?sid=yt
Like "The Late Show" on Facebook: http://on.fb.me/1df139Y
Follow "The Late Show" on X: http://bit.ly/1dMzZzG
Follow "The Late Show" on Instagram: http://bit.ly/29wfREj

Watch The Late Show with Stephen Colbert weeknights at 11:35 PM ET/10:35 PM CT. Only on CBS.

---
Stephen Colbert brings his signature satire and comedy to THE LATE SHOW with STEPHEN COLBERT, the #1 show in late night, where he talks with an eclectic mix of guests about what is new and relevant in the worlds of politics, entertainment, business, music, technology and more. Featuring bandleader Louis Cato and “THE LATE SHOW band,” the Peabody Award-winning and Emmy Award-nominated show is broadcast from the historic Ed Sullivan Theater. Stephen Colbert took over as host, executive producer and writer of THE LATE SHOW on Sept. 8, 2015.

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat II | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's called Mortal Kombat (II).
Mortal Kombat II – only in theaters and @imax October 24. #MortalKombatMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favorite champions—now joined by Johnny Cage himself—are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/Broken Road Production, a Fireside Films Production, Mortal Kombat II.  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAX® across North America on October 24, 2025, and internationally beginning 22 October 2025.

snippet.title: Tron: Ares | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the brand-new trailer for Tron: Ares and experience it in theaters, filmed for IMAX, October 10.
 
Tron: Ares follows a highly sophisticated Program, Ares, who is sent from the digital world into the real world on a dangerous mission, marking humankind’s first encounter with A.I. beings. The feature film is directed by Joachim Rønning and stars Jared Leto, Greta Lee, Evan Peters, Hasan Minhaj, Jodie Turner-Smith, Arturo Castro, Cameron Monaghan, with Gillian Anderson, and Jeff Bridges. Sean Bailey, Jeffrey Silver, Justin Springer, Jared Leto, Emma Ludbrook and Steven Lisberger are the producers, with Russell Allen serving as executive producer.

Grammy®-award winning rock band Nine Inch Nails composed the score for “Tron: Ares,” and today, the band dropped "As Alive As You Need Me To Be" —the soundtrack album’s first single and the first official music from the band in five years. Listen to "As Alive As You Need Me To Be” and view the visualizer: https://nineinchnails.lnk.to/AAAYNMTB. The track is featured in the new trailer for “Tron: Ares.”
 
“Tron: Ares (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack),” featuring all original music by Nine Inch Nails, will be released on September 19 via Interscope Records. The release marks the first-ever film score by the pioneering band, although bandmates Trent Reznor and Atticus Ross have composed 20 scores under their own names, winning two Oscars®, three Golden Globes®, a GRAMMY® and an Emmy® in the process.
 
ALBUM: https://NineInchNails.lnk.to/TRONAres
SINGLE: https://NineInchNails.lnk.to/AAAYNMTB
LYRIC VIDEO: https://youtu.be/-Sj-FmI5JfA

snippet.title: Stranger Things 5 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every battle has led to this.

More about Stranger Things 5:
The fall of 1987. Hawkins is scarred by the opening of the Rifts, and our heroes are united by a single goal: find and kill Vecna. But he has vanished — his whereabouts and plans unknown. Complicating their mission, the government has placed the town under military quarantine and intensified its hunt for Eleven, forcing her back into hiding. As the anniversary of Will’s disappearance approaches, so does a heavy, familiar dread. The final battle is looming — and with it, a darkness more powerful and more deadly than anything they’ve faced before. To end this nightmare, they’ll need everyone — the full party — standing together, one last time.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81297917

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

'You'll Be Alright, Kid' out now: https://alexwarren.lnk.to/YoullBeAlrightKid

Lyrics:
Hear the clock ticking on the wall
Losing sleep losing track of the tears I cry
Every drop is a waterfall
Every breath is a break in the riptide
Oh, how long
Has it been I
Don’t know
But it
Feels like an eternity
Since I had you here with me
Since I had to learn to be
Someone you don't know 
To be with you in paradise
What I wouldn’t sacrifice
Why’d you have to chase the light
Somewhere I can’t go
As I walk this world alone
As I walk this world alone
Another glimpse of what coulda been
Another dream of the way that it never was
Falling back in the wilderness
Waking up rubbing salt in the cut
Oh, how long
Has it been I
Don’t know
But it
Feels like an eternity
Since I had you here with me
Since I had to learn to be
Someone you don't know 
To be with you in paradise
What I wouldn’t sacrifice
Why’d you have to chase the light
Somewhere I can’t go
As I walk this world alone
As I walk this world alone

It’s an endless night
It’s a starless sky
It’s a hell that I call home
It’s a long goodbye
On the other side
Of the only life I know

And it feels like an eternity
Since I had you here with me
Since I had to learn to be
Someone you don't know 

To be with you in paradise

นักเดินทาง แล้วเจอกันนะ!
(รหัสแลกรับในโปรแกรมพิเศษนี้จะหมดอายุในวันที่ 21 ก.ค. เวลา 11:00 น. (UTC+7) อย่าพลาดเวลาในการแลกรับนะ~)

id.description:

Hari ini, kita kembali ke mesin penjual ikan LIVE — dan kali ini, kita membeli semuanya. Dari ikan air asin yang unik hingga ikan misterius, mesin ini penuh dengan makhluk laut eksotis… dan kita bahkan menemukan tombol baru berlabel Telur Misteri. Kita pernah mendapatkan belut moray, telur hiu, dan bahkan predator berbahaya dari mesin ini sebelumnya… tapi ini mungkin hasil buruan terliar kita sejauh ini. Akankah tombolnya berfungsi? Vandaag zijn we terug bij de LIVE visautomaat — en dit keer kopen we van alles. Van gekke zoutwatervissen tot mysterieuze vissen, deze automaat zit vol met exotische zeedieren… en we hebben zelfs een gloednieuwe knop gevonden met het label Mystery Egg. snippet.title: Coldplay’s ‘kiss cam’ exposes apparent AFFAIR between mortified CEO and HR Chief
snippet.description:
A “kiss cam” moment broadcast at a Coldplay concert struck a scandalous note when it apparently exposed a cheating tech tycoon and his head of HR mistress, as the band’s frontman Chris Martin mused they must be “having an affair.” They have since been identified as Astronomer CEO Andy Byron and the firm’s chief human resources officer, Kristin Cabot. 

#coldplay #affair #AndyByron #KristinCabot

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 2 - Official 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer (2025) Karl Urban
snippet.description:
Don't miss the 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer for Mortal Kombat 2, the upcoming action film based on the hit Mortal Kombat game IP distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures. Take a look at the in-universe film trailer for Uncaged Fury starring the one and only Johnny Cage, portrayed by Karl Urban. 

Uncaged Fury sees the legendary Johnny Cage take on a band of goons with ease, making use of pipes, fast-paced combat skills, and an aura unlike any other.

Mortal Kombat 2 is in theaters on October 24.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Reuniting With My Family and Girlfriend After 2 Years
snippet.description:
MY BROTHER IS HOME!! 😭✈️ Emotional Missionary Homecoming After 2 Years

After two years away, Brock is finally HOME!! He spent the last year and a half serving in Boston, Massachusetts, and this vlog captures the unforgettable moments leading up to his return. From packing his (very heavy) bags and saying goodbye to mission friends, to getting paired with a final companion—his journey back was emotional and full of meaning.

Back at home, I was getting everything ready for his arrival—stocking the pantry (per Brock’s special request), grabbing some of his favorite foods, and prepping the house for a big surprise. We stayed up late making posters (yes, including a hilarious “marry me” one and some Fortnite-themed signs 😂) and decorated everything to make his homecoming extra special.

He landed in Salt Lake City, and the moment he walked through those airport doors… we were all in tears. Our mom cried, and the biggest surprise of all—his girlfriend was there to meet him even though he thought she’d still be out of town 👀

Once we got home, Brock saw his room for the first time, opened his welcome-back gift basket, and we wrapped up the perfect day with a Bees baseball game as a family. It was one of those days we’ll never forget.

snippet.title: We Spent 48 Hours With MLB All-Stars!
snippet.description:
We Spent 2 Days with MLB All-Stars at the 95th All-Star Game in Atlanta, Georgia! We hope you enjoy this video and consider subscribing if you do, it really helps us out! 🦾

We’ve got an action packed video this week as we attended the Home Run Derby and All-Star Game, along with media day and the red carpet show. We saw familiar faces and met a bunch of guys for the first time and got to congratulate them on their All-Star nomination, which was so cool. We had a bunch of interviews and hilarious moments throughout the entire trip, so be sure to stick around to the end of the video!

We said what’s up and interviewed a bunch of players from both the National League and American League, including; Kyle Tucker, Pete Crow-Armstrong, Aroldis Chapman, Logan Webb, Corbin Carroll, Jacob Misiorowski, Jazz Chisholm Jr., Byron Buxton, Steven Kwan, MacKenzie Gore, James Wood, Jacob Wilson, Brendon Donovan, Ryan O’Hearn, Hunter Goodman, Brandon Lowe, Zach McKinstry, 

Thank you so much to all of the players for their time, we’re so excited to see how all of them continue to ball out in the second half. Also thank you so much to MLB for giving us credentialed access to talk to the games biggest stars on the biggest stage. Finally, thank you to you all for your continued support ❤️ none of this is possible without you guys and we are so grateful to be able to go on these adventures because of you all. Shoutout to everyone that said what’s up to us on the trip, Atlanta was amazing. Stay tuned as we’ve got a LOT more content coming the rest of the summer💯


If you enjoyed this video and want to see more like it, make sure to SUBSCRIBE! The support from everyone who watches our videos means so much to us and we're going to continue to grind to promote the incredible game of baseball and all the culture and personalities within it!

SUBSCRIBE: https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCV9bUn2gOlnMHpYNbohxYaA

Follow us on INSTAGRAM and TIK TOK @batboysbaseball for the coolest  baseball content you’re going to find!!!!

INSTAGRAM: https://instagram.com/batboysbaseball
TIK TOK: https://vm.tiktok.com/wgsBao/

snippet.title: REDstreams — Update 2.3 Overview
snippet.description:
There it is, chooms! 

Another episode of REDstreams is hitting the streets of Night City! 

Join us this Wednesday, July 16th at 5:00 PM as we’re taking the wheel to show you some of the most important features coming in Patch 2.3.

Paweł Sasko, Cyberpunk 2 Associate Game Director, and Adrien Jouannet, Lead Designer at Virtuos, will guide us through what’s under the hood of the latest update.

And no surprises here: Amelia Korzycka and Alicja Kozera are back in the driver’s seat.

snippet.title: Clipse on "Let God Sort Em Out,” Pharrell, Jay-Z & Def Jam | Fat Joe, Jadakiss, Pusha T & Malice
snippet.description:
Fat Joe and Jadakiss are joined by Pusha T and Malice, a.k.a. Clipse, to dive into their rap careers and their new album ‘Let God Sort Em Out.’ They discuss how they originally linked up with super producer Pharrell Williams and how he has been a huge part of their sound from the very beginning. Next, Pusha and Malice break down why they left Def Jam over the Kendrick Lamar track on their new album, explaining that in no way is it a beef record, but that politics and optics were the real reason Def Jam had a problem with it. They also thank Jay-Z and Roc Nation for stepping up to do the distribution and explain why they decided that the first track be "The Birds Don't Sing,” a tribute to their late mother and father, featuring John Legend.
(Recorded on June 17, 2025)

snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Sagat Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Sagat returns on August 5 and he demands an audience with you adoring pests.

Heed his summons before he pummels you with regal uppercuts and majestic fireballs.

The Year 3 Character Pass and Ultimate Pass are now available! Owners of the Year 3 Character / Ultimate Pass will automatically get access to Sagat and the Proud Spire stage when he releases. The Year 3 Character Pass will include 4 characters (Sagat, C. Viper, Alex, and Ingrid), Outfit 1 Colors 3-10 for those characters, and 3000 Drive Tickets. The Year 3 Ultimate Pass includes everything in the Character Pass plus Outfit 2 and 3 Colors 3-10, an additional stage, and 2800 more Drive Tickets for a total of 5800. All the content from these passes will unlock as they release throughout Year 3.

*Year 3 Character Pass and Year 3 Ultimate Pass for Nintendo Switch 2 will be available for pre-order until August 4, 2025. Please note that additional content included in the pass will unlock starting from August 5, 2025 based on the character release schedule for Year 3.

snippet.title: Why Modern Gaming Sucks - You Own Nothing, And You're Not Happy
snippet.description: Live service models. Endless updates. Microtransactions. Mandatory patches. Always online. Gaming has become a bloated, money-grabbing disaster where you increasingly don't even own the game you've supposedly bought. And at any moment, the company who rent it to you could decide to shut it down. Is it any wonder the Stop Killing Games movement has become so huge, so quickly?

I discuss the new clips in the preview which showed Vecna returning and looking different, Jonathan potentially dying in the upside down, Will being connected to The Mind Flayer and being taken by Vecna, Eddie's grave being defaced, the return of the Demodogs, the portal in Hawkins Library to the upside down and the final battle with Vecna and Eleven. snippet.title: IMPOSSIBLE 400KM CAPE YORK TRACK - Bogged to doors & out of ideas
snippet.description:
This is one of the wildest, most beautiful & most dangerous places to take a 4WD. Out here, you don’t walk the bog holes first… because this is croc country. 🐊

We’ve been dreaming of this trip for over a decade: 400km of low range through some of the most remote terrain in Australia and half of it might never have been driven before.

We’re going West to East – right across Cape York – kicking off in Pormpuraaw and heading deep into unknown territory. Bottomless black soil, brutal climbs, and tracks that have completely vanished. This one’s going to push us, and the rigs, to the absolute limit. 😳

We’ve got the convoy to take it on… and we’re not just doing it for the challenge. There’s talk of a hidden paradise out on the coast – and we’re going to find it.

Welcome to Far North Queensland.

📱 FOLLOW OUR SOCIALS for behind the scenes content

Shaun, Graham, Jock, & Jesse - formerly with 4WD Action - have been delivering the best off-road content in Australia for 20+ years. From epic car builds & 4x4 tips to exploring iconic spots like Fraser Island, Utah, The Kimberley, Colorado, The Rubicon Trail & The Simpson Desert, we create content for every off-roader. We've even hit the tracks with the legends from Donut Media! Whether you’re rocking a fully modified Toyota LandCruiser or just getting started with your Hilux or Ranger, we’ve got you covered for all things 4WD and adventure.

#4wd247 #4x4 #mechanic #adventure #explore #capeyork #travel #outdoors #toughwheeling #bogged #boghole #touring #overlanding #toyota #mazda #TRAVEL25EP09

Not IMPOSSIBLE 400KM CAPE YORK TRACK - Bogged to doors & out of ideas, But OUR WORST BOGGED MOMENTS & EPIC RECOVERIES! Bent recovery points, 6hr winches, sleeping in mud!, But 4WDs ABANDONED in Worst Desert Flood… Desperate Escape Attempt, But THE WETTEST WE'VE SEEN CAPE YORK... RAGING rivers & bottomless mud - 1st 4WDs down Tele Track 2023, But MOST BOGGED WE’VE EVER BEEN.. Cape York - Did we all get out? Digging into the night, But ABANDONED CAPE YORK TRACK NOT DRIVEN IN 60yrs... We attempt it in monsoon rain!, But $1,000 HiLux takes on CAPE YORK! • Old Tele Track, But VW Amarok Tackling Gunshot Creek Sept 2015, But DROWNED 4WD! Our most insane recovery ever – did we rescue it? Moreton Island like you’ve never seen, But CAPE YORK RIVER CROSSING goes horribly WRONG... SOOTY FLOATS, WATER OVER SEATS & the engine stops… or any other video like 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media or Mighty Car Mods would make. This is a video where Shaun Whale & Graham Cahill take on Cape York East to West!

ja.title: 不可能な400kmケープヨークトラック - ドアまで泥沼、アイデアも尽きた
ja.description:
ここは4WDで行くには最もワイルドで、最も美しく、そして最も危険な場所の一つです。ここはワニの生息地なので、沼地を最初から歩くなんて考えられません。🐊

私たちは10年以上前からこの旅を夢見てきました。オーストラリアで最も辺鄙な地形を低速で400km走り、その半分はおそらく誰も走ったことのない道です。

西から東へ、ケープヨークを横切り、ポンプラウをスタートして未知の領域へと深く入り込みます。底なしの黒土、過酷な登り坂、そして完全に消えてしまった道。この旅は私たちと4WDを極限まで追い込むことになるでしょう。😳

私たちはこの旅に挑むためのコンボイを揃えています…そして、ただ挑戦したいだけではありません。海岸沿いには隠された楽園があるという噂があり、私たちはそれを探しに行きます。

ファー・ノース・クイーンズランドへようこそ。

ケープヨーク・トラック400km、不可能じゃない！ ドアまで泥濘、アイデアも尽きたけど、最悪の泥濘と壮大なリカバリー！ リカバリーポイントは曲がり、ウインチは6時間もかかり、泥の中で寝泊まり！ 最悪の砂漠の洪水で4WDは置き去りに… 必死の脱出を試みるも、ケープヨークは今まで見た中で最も雨が降り… 激流と底なしの泥 - 2023年、初めて4WDでテレトラックを下るも、今までで一番泥濘… ケープヨーク ― 全員脱出できたかな？夜道を掘るが、60年間誰も走っていないケープヨークの廃道…モンスーンの雨の中挑戦！1,000ドルのハイラックスがケープヨークに挑む！ • 古いテレトラック、しかしVWアマロックが2015年9月にガンショットクリークに挑戦、しかし水没した4WD！ これまでで最もクレイジーな復旧 – 救出できたのか？ 見たこともないようなモートン島、しかしケープヨーク川の横断はひどい結果に… すすだらけのフロート、シート上水浸し、そしてエンジン停止… または、4WD 24/7、The Grand Tour、Matts Off Road Recovery、Donut Media、Mighty Car Modsなどの他のビデオ。これは、ショーン・ホエールとグラハム・ケイヒルがケープヨークを東から西に横断するビデオです！

en.title: IMPOSSIBLE 400KM CAPE YORK TRACK - Bogged to doors & out of ideas
en.description:
This is one of the wildest, most beautiful & most dangerous places to take a 4WD. Out here, you don’t walk the bog holes first… because this is croc country. 🐊

We’ve been dreaming of this trip for over a decade: 400km of low range through some of the most remote terrain in Australia and half of it might never have been driven before.

We’re going West to East – right across Cape York – kicking off in Pormpuraaw and heading deep into unknown territory. Bottomless black soil, brutal climbs, and tracks that have completely vanished. This one’s going to push us, and the rigs, to the absolute limit. 😳

We’ve got the convoy to take it on… and we’re not just doing it for the challenge. There’s talk of a hidden paradise out on the coast – and we’re going to find it.

Welcome to Far North Queensland.

es-US.title: PISTA IMPOSIBLE DE 400 KM DE CAPE YORK - Atascado hasta las puertas y sin ideas
es-US.description:
Este es uno de los lugares más salvajes, hermosos y peligrosos para un 4x4. Aquí, no se camina primero por los pantanos… porque esto es tierra de cocodrilos. 🐊

Llevamos más de una década soñando con este viaje: 400 km de baja autonomía a través de algunos de los terrenos más remotos de Australia, y la mitad de ellos quizá nunca antes se hayan recorrido.

Vamos de oeste a este, cruzando el Cabo York, comenzando en Pormpuraaw y adentrándonos en territorio desconocido. Tierra negra sin fondo, subidas brutales y pistas que han desaparecido por completo. Este viaje nos va a llevar, a nosotros y a los vehículos, al límite absoluto. 😳

Tenemos el convoy para afrontarlo… y no lo hacemos solo por el desafío. Se habla de un paraíso escondido en la costa, y lo vamos a encontrar.

Bienvenidos al extremo norte de Queensland.

fr-FR.title: PISTE IMPOSSIBLE DE 400 KM DE CAPE YORK - Enlisé jusqu'aux portes et à court d'idées
fr-FR.description:
C'est l'un des endroits les plus sauvages, les plus beaux et les plus dangereux pour un 4x4. Ici, on ne traverse pas d'abord les marécages… car c'est le pays des crocodiles. 🐊

On rêve de ce voyage depuis plus de dix ans : 400 km de faible autonomie à travers des régions parmi les plus reculées d'Australie, dont la moitié n'aurait peut-être jamais été parcourue auparavant.

On file d'ouest en est, en traversant le cap York, en commençant par Pormpuraaw et en s'enfonçant dans des terres inconnues. Une terre noire sans fond, des montées abruptes et des pistes complètement disparues. Ce voyage va nous pousser, nous et les véhicules, à nos limites absolues. 😳

On a le convoi pour s'y aventurer… et on ne le fait pas seulement pour le défi. On parle d'un paradis caché sur la côte, et on va le trouver.

Bienvenue dans l'extrême nord du Queensland.

ko.title: 불가능한 400km 케이프 요크 트랙 - 문이 막히고 아이디어가 고갈됨
ko.description:
이곳은 사륜구동차를 타기에 가장 거칠고 아름다우면서도 위험한 곳 중 하나입니다. 여기서는 먼저 늪지대를 걷지 않습니다… 악어 서식지니까요. 🐊

10년 넘게 이 여행을 꿈꿔왔습니다. 호주에서 가장 외딴 지형을 통과하는 400km의 저속 주행 코스인데, 그중 절반은 아마 이전에는 한 번도 운전해 본 적이 없었을 겁니다.

서쪽에서 동쪽으로, 케이프 요크를 가로질러 폼푸라우에서 출발하여 미지의 땅 깊숙한 곳으로 향합니다. 끝없이 펼쳐진 검은 흙, 험난한 오르막길, 그리고 완전히 사라진 트랙들. 이곳은 우리와 우리 차량을 극한으로 몰아붙일 것입니다. 😳

이 여정을 함께할 차량들이 있습니다… 단순히 도전을 위한 여정이 아닙니다. 해안가에 숨겨진 낙원이 있다는 소문이 돌고 있고, 우리는 반드시 그것을 찾아낼 것입니다.

퀸즐랜드 최북단에 오신 것을 환영합니다.

불가능하지 않은 400km 케이프요크 트랙 - 문까지 늪지대에 빠져 아이디어도 없었지만, 최악의 늪지대 순간과 멋진 회복! 휘어진 회복 지점, 6시간 윈치, 진흙탕 잠! 하지만 최악의 사막 홍수에 버려져 버린 4륜구동차… 필사적인 탈출 시도였지만, 케이프요크에서 본 것 중 가장 습한 곳… 거센 강물과 끝없는 진흙 - 2023년 텔레 트랙에서 4륜구동차가 처음으로 진입했지만, 역대 가장 늪지대에 빠졌습니다. 케이프요크 - 모두 탈출했나요? 밤을 뚫고 나가지만, 60년 동안 한 번도 달리지 않은 버려진 케이프 요크 트랙... 몬순 비 속에서 도전해 봤습니다! 1,000달러짜리 하이럭스가 케이프 요크에 도전합니다! • 낡은 텔레 트랙, 2015년 9월 건샷 크릭을 헤쳐나가는 VW 아마록, 그리고 물에 잠긴 4륜구동차! 역대급으로 정신없는 구조 작업 - 과연 구조했을까요? 지금껏 본 적 없는 모레턴 섬, 하지만 케이프 요크 강을 건너는 건 완전히 엉망이 되었습니다... 그을음이 떠다니고, 좌석 위로 물이 차오르고, 엔진이 멈췄습니다... 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media, Mighty Car Mods 같은 영상이라면 누구든 만들 수 있을 겁니다. 숀 웨일과 그레이엄 케이힐이 케이프 요크를 동서로 누비는 영상입니다!

pl.title: NIEMOŻLIWY 400-KMOWY TOR NA PRZYLĄDKU JORK – UTARTY PO DRZWI I BRAK POMYSŁÓW
pl.description:
To jedno z najdzikszych, najpiękniejszych i najniebezpieczniejszych miejsc na jazdę samochodem terenowym. Tutaj nie trzeba najpierw przedzierać się przez bagna… bo to kraina krokodyli. 🐊

Marzyliśmy o tej wyprawie od ponad dekady: 400 km nizinnych terenów przez jedne z najbardziej odległych terenów Australii, z czego połowa mogła nigdy wcześniej nie zostać przejechana.

Jedziemy z zachodu na wschód – prosto przez Przylądek Jork – startując w Pormpuraaw i wkraczając w głąb nieznanego terytorium. Bezdenna czarna ziemia, brutalne podjazdy i trasy, które całkowicie zniknęły. Ta wyprawa zmusi nas i nasze pojazdy do absolutnej granicy możliwości. 😳

Mamy konwój, który to zniesie… i nie robimy tego tylko dla wyzwania. Mówi się o ukrytym raju na wybrzeżu – i zamierzamy go znaleźć.

Witamy w dalekiej północy Queensland.

id.title: JALUR CAPE YORK 400KM YANG MUSTAHIL - Terjebak di pintu & kehabisan ide
id.description:
Ini salah satu tempat terliar, terindah, & paling berbahaya untuk mengendarai kendaraan 4WD. Di sini, jangan masuk ke lubang rawa dulu... karena ini negeri buaya. 🐊

Kami sudah memimpikan perjalanan ini selama lebih dari satu dekade: 400 km di dataran rendah melewati beberapa medan paling terpencil di Australia dan setengahnya mungkin belum pernah kami lalui sebelumnya.

Kami akan pergi dari Barat ke Timur – tepat melintasi Cape York – dimulai di Pormpuraaw dan menuju jauh ke wilayah yang belum dikenal. Tanah hitam tak berdasar, tanjakan brutal, dan trek yang telah lenyap sepenuhnya. Yang ini akan mendorong kami, dan rig, hingga batas maksimal. 😳

Kami punya konvoi untuk melakukannya... dan kami tidak melakukannya hanya untuk tantangan. Ada pembicaraan tentang surga tersembunyi di pesisir – dan kami akan menemukannya.

Selamat datang di Queensland Utara Jauh.

de-DE.title: UNMÖGLICHE 400 KM CAPE YORK TRACK - Bis an die Türen festgefahren und ohne Ideen
de-DE.description:
Dies ist einer der wildesten, schönsten und gefährlichsten Orte für einen Allrad-Rennwagen. Hier geht man nicht erst durch die Moorlöcher … denn hier sind Krokodil-Gebiete. 🐊

Wir träumen seit über einem Jahrzehnt von dieser Reise: 400 km im niedrigen Gelände durch einige der abgelegensten Gegenden Australiens, von denen die Hälfte vielleicht noch nie zuvor befahren wurde.

Wir fahren von West nach Ost – quer durch Cape York –, starten in Pormpuraaw und dringen tief in unbekanntes Gebiet vor. Bodenloser schwarzer Boden, brutale Anstiege und völlig verschwundene Pisten. Diese Reise wird uns und die Fahrzeuge bis ans absolute Limit fordern. 😳

Wir haben den Konvoi, um es zu schaffen … und wir machen es nicht nur wegen der Herausforderung. Es gibt Gerüchte über ein verborgenes Paradies an der Küste – und wir werden es finden.

Willkommen im äußersten Norden von Queensland.

#4wd247 #4x4 #Mechaniker #Abenteuer #Entdecken #CapeYork #Reisen #Outdoor #ToughWheeling #Festgefahren #Sumpfloch #Touring #Overlanding #Toyota #Mazda #TRAVEL25EP09

Keine unmöglichen 400 km auf dem Cape York Track – Bis zum Anschlag festgefahren und ohne Ideen. Aber unsere schlimmsten Festgefahren-Momente und epischen Bergungen! Verbogene Abschleppösen, 6-Stunden-Winden, im Schlamm schlafen! Aber Geländewagen bei der schlimmsten Wüstenflut zurückgelassen… Verzweifelter Fluchtversuch, aber der nasseste, den wir je in Cape York gesehen haben… Tosende Flüsse und bodenloser Schlamm – die ersten Geländewagen auf dem Tele Track 2023, aber so festgefahren, wie wir es noch nie waren… Cape York – Sind wir alle rausgekommen? Bis in die Nacht gegraben, aber die verlassene Cape York-Strecke wurde seit 60 Jahren nicht mehr befahren ... Wir haben es im Monsunregen versucht! Aber ein 1.000-Dollar-HiLux nimmt es mit Cape York auf! • Alte Tele-Strecke, aber VW Amarok bewältigt Gunshot Creek, September 2015, aber ein GETRUNKENER 4WD! Unsere verrückteste Bergung aller Zeiten – haben wir ihn gerettet? Moreton Island, wie Sie es noch nie gesehen haben, aber die Flussüberquerung von Cape York geht schrecklich schief ... Rußige Schwimmer, Wasser über den Sitzen und der Motor bleibt stehen … oder jedes andere Video, wie es 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media oder Mighty Car Mods machen würden. Dies ist ein Video, in dem Shaun Whale und Graham Cahill Cape York von Ost nach West in Angriff nehmen!

it.title: IMPOSSIBILE PISTA DI CAPE YORK DA 400 KM - Impantanato fino alle porte e senza idee
it.description:
Questo è uno dei luoghi più selvaggi, belli e pericolosi per un fuoristrada. Qui, non si cammina prima nelle paludi... perché questa è la terra dei coccodrilli. 🐊

Sognavamo questo viaggio da oltre un decennio: 400 km a basso consumo attraverso alcuni dei territori più remoti dell'Australia, metà dei quali forse non erano mai stati percorsi prima.

Andremo da ovest a est, attraversando Capo York, partendo da Pormpuraaw e addentrandoci in territori sconosciuti. Terra nera senza fondo, salite brutali e sentieri completamente scomparsi. Questo viaggio spingerà noi e i nostri mezzi al limite assoluto. 😳

Abbiamo il convoglio per affrontarlo... e non lo facciamo solo per la sfida. Si parla di un paradiso nascosto sulla costa, e lo troveremo.

Benvenuti nel Far North Queensland.

hi.title: असंभव 400 किमी का केप यॉर्क ट्रैक - दरवाजे तक फंस गया और विचारों से बाहर
hi.description:
यह 4WD लेने के लिए सबसे जंगली, सबसे खूबसूरत और सबसे खतरनाक जगहों में से एक है। यहाँ, आपको पहले दलदली गड्ढों में नहीं जाना पड़ता... क्योंकि यह मगरमच्छों का देश है। 🐊

हम एक दशक से भी ज़्यादा समय से इस यात्रा का सपना देख रहे हैं: ऑस्ट्रेलिया के कुछ सबसे दुर्गम इलाकों से होकर 400 किलोमीटर की कम दूरी की यात्रा, और इसका आधा हिस्सा शायद पहले कभी गाड़ी से नहीं तय किया गया हो।

हम पश्चिम से पूर्व की ओर जा रहे हैं - केप यॉर्क के ठीक पार - पोर्मपुराव से शुरुआत करते हुए और अनजान इलाकों में गहराई तक जा रहे हैं। अथाह काली मिट्टी, कठिन चढ़ाई, और पूरी तरह से गायब हो चुके रास्ते। यह हमें और हमारे रिग्स को पूरी तरह से चरम सीमा तक धकेल देगा। 😳

हमारे पास इसे करने के लिए एक काफिला है... और हम इसे सिर्फ़ चुनौती के लिए नहीं कर रहे हैं। तट पर एक छिपे हुए स्वर्ग की चर्चा हो रही है - और हम उसे ढूँढ़ने जा रहे हैं।

सुदूर उत्तरी क्वींसलैंड में आपका स्वागत है।

nl-NL.title: ONMOGELIJKE 400 KM CAPE YORK-TRACK - Vastgelopen en zonder ideeën
nl-NL.description:
Dit is een van de wildste, mooiste en gevaarlijkste plekken om met een 4x4 naartoe te gaan. Hier hoef je niet eerst door de moerassen te lopen... want dit is krokodillenland. 🐊

We dromen al meer dan tien jaar van deze reis: 400 km aan lage snelheden door een van de meest afgelegen gebieden van Australië, waarvan de helft misschien nog nooit eerder is gereden.

We gaan van west naar oost – dwars door Cape York – beginnen in Pormpuraaw en gaan diep onbekend gebied in. Bodemloze zwarte aarde, brute beklimmingen en paden die volledig verdwenen zijn. Deze gaat ons, en de wagens, tot het uiterste drijven. 😳

We hebben het konvooi om het aan te gaan... en we doen het niet alleen voor de uitdaging. Er wordt gesproken over een verborgen paradijs aan de kust - en we gaan het vinden.

Welkom in Far North Queensland.

Graven in de nacht, maar VERLATEN CAPE YORK TRACK AL 60 JAAR NIET GERIJDEN... We proberen het in de moessonregen!, maar een HiLux van $1.000 neemt het op tegen CAPE YORK! • Oude Tele Track, maar VW Amarok trotseert Gunshot Creek in september 2015, maar VERDRONKEN 4WD! Onze meest waanzinnige berging ooit - hebben we het gered? Moreton Island zoals je het nog nooit hebt gezien, maar de CAPE YORK RIVER CROSSING gaat vreselijk MIS... ROET DRIJFT, WATER OVER DE STOELEN EN DE MOTOR SLAAT AF... of een andere video zoals 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media of Mighty Car Mods zou maken. Dit is een video waarin Shaun Whale en Graham Cahill het op nemen tegen Cape York van oost naar west!

pt-BR.title: TRILHA IMPOSSÍVEL DE 400 KM NO CABO YORK - Atolado nas portas e sem ideias
pt-BR.description:
Este é um dos lugares mais selvagens, bonitos e perigosos para se levar um 4x4. Aqui, você não anda primeiro pelos pântanos... porque esta é a terra dos crocodilos. 🐊

Sonhamos com esta viagem há mais de uma década: 400 km de baixa altitude por alguns dos terrenos mais remotos da Austrália, e metade dela talvez nunca tenha sido percorrida antes.

Vamos de oeste para leste – atravessando o Cabo York – começando em Pormpuraaw e nos aprofundando em território desconhecido. Solo negro sem fundo, subidas brutais e trilhas que desapareceram completamente. Esta viagem vai nos levar, e aos equipamentos, ao limite absoluto. 😳

Temos o comboio para encarar... e não estamos fazendo isso apenas pelo desafio. Fala-se de um paraíso escondido na costa – e vamos encontrá-lo.

Bem-vindos ao Extremo Norte de Queensland.

Shaun, Graham, Jock e Jesse - anteriormente da 4WD Action - produzem o melhor conteúdo off-road da Austrália há mais de 20 anos. De montagens épicas de carros e dicas sobre veículos 4x4 a explorações de lugares icônicos como a Ilha Fraser, em Utah, Kimberley, no Colorado, a Trilha Rubicon e o Deserto Simpson, criamos conteúdo para todos os amantes do off-road. Já fomos às pistas com as lendas da Donut Media! Seja você um Toyota LandCruiser totalmente modificado ou apenas iniciando com sua Hilux ou Ranger, temos tudo o que você precisa para 4x4 e aventura.

#4wd247 #4x4 #mecânico #aventura #explorar #capeyork #viagem #ao ar livre #difícil #atolado #buraco #turismo #overlanding #toyota #mazda #TRAVEL25EP09

Não é IMPOSSÍVEL 400 KM DE TRILHA DO CABO YORK - Atolado até as portas e sem ideias, mas NOSSOS PIORES MOMENTOS DE ATOLAMENTO E RECUPERAÇÕES ÉPICAS! Pontos de recuperação tortos, guinchos de 6 horas, dormindo na lama!, mas 4x4 ABANDONADOS na pior enchente do deserto... Tentativa de fuga desesperada, mas A MAIS CHUVOSA QUE JÁ VIMOS O CABO YORK... Rios caudalosos e lama sem fundo - Primeiros 4x4 na Tele Track em 2023, mas o MAIS ATOLADO QUE JÁ PASSEIMOS... Cabo York - Será que todos nós conseguimos sair? Cavando na noite, Mas a PISTA ABANDONADA DE CAPE YORK NÃO É DIRIGIDA HÁ 60 ANOS... Tentamos na chuva de monção!, Mas uma HiLux de US$ 1.000 encara CAPE YORK! • Antiga Pista Tele, Mas a VW Amarok Enfrentando Gunshot Creek em Setembro de 2015, Mas AFOGADO COM 4WD! Nossa recuperação mais insana de todos os tempos – será que a resgatamos? Ilha Moreton como você nunca viu, Mas a TRAVESSIA DO RIO CAPE YORK dá terrivelmente ERRADO... FULIGEM BOIA, ÁGUA SOBRE OS BANCOS e o motor para... ou qualquer outro vídeo como 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media ou Mighty Car Mods daria certo. Este é um vídeo onde Shaun Whale e Graham Cahill encaram Cape York de Leste a Oeste!

snippet.title: The 'Zombies 4' Cast Talk Co-Star Crushes & Cringe Auditions | Pass the Popcorn | Seventeen
snippet.description:
Milo Manheim, Meg Donnelly, Malachi Barton, and Freya Skye are trading zombies and fangs for brutally honest confessions in this episode of “Pass the Popcorn.” Can the ‘Zombies 4: Dawn of the Vampires’ cast handle the heat offscreen as they face a mouthful of shady questions (and popcorn)? With only one pass allowed, nothing is off-limits as they call out each other’s toxic traits, expose cringe audition memories, and reveal the wildest DMs they’ve ever received. Between bites, the co-stars open up about awkward fan run-ins, debate which DCOMs are lowkey overrated, and—spoiler alert—someone admits they’ve never even watched the ‘Zombies’ movies outside of the premiere 👀.
 
Stream ‘Zombies 4: Dawn of the Vampires’ on Disney+.

snippet.title: Donkey Kong Bananza - Nintendo Switch 2 - Digital Foundry Review
snippet.description:
Following up on Mario Kart World for the next big Nintendo Switch 2 exclusive was never going to be easy - but it turns out that Donkey Kong Bananza is nothing short of a triumph. John Linneman dives deeply into the game's technology, performance and handheld experience - and has much to say about the high quality of the gameplay.

Join the DF Supporter Program for pristine video downloads, behind the scenes content, early access to new videos, early access to DF Direct Weekly and much, much more: https://bit.ly/3jEGjvx

snippet.title: Love Island's Nic & Olandria APOLOGIZE to Nicolandria Nation After Denying Feelings for Each Other
snippet.description: 'Love Island USA' season 7 runners-up Nic Vansteenberghe and Olandria Carthen chat with ET's Brice Sander following the finale, now streaming on Peacock. The pair address denying their feelings for one another after a steamy kiss in Soul Ties, explaining it was a defense mechanism to protect the people they were then-interested in, Cierra Ortega and Taylor Williams. They share where they stand with the ex-Islanders now and whether they're ready to label each other boyfriend and girlfriend ahead of the soon-to-tape reunion, set to premiere on Aug. 25 on Peacock.

snippet.title: Investigating the DKOldies Scam...
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more! https://www.youtube.com/austinevans
Check out our @thisis channel! https://www.youtube.com/thisis
As well as the @Denki channel! https://www.youtube.com/@Denki
Instagram: https://instagram.com/austinnotduncan
Threads: https://www.threads.net/@austinnotduncan

Is DKOldies REALLY the retro gaming paradise they claim to be? After spending over $1,300 on vintage consoles and games, the results were...not great. From broken Wii Us with cracked vents to Xbox 360s that literally scratch your discs, this investigation reveals what you're actually getting for your money. Plus, we test their warranty claims and trade-in process with some eye-opening results. Are they worth those premium prices or should you look elsewhere for your retro gaming fix?

0:00 Ordering

3:37 Wii U

7:55 PS2 Slim
11:06 GameCube
14:43 Xbox 360
17:50 Nintendo Switch
20:10 Trade In and Warranty
23:33 Xbox 360 Round 2
24:53 Wii U Round 2
26:27 Conclusion

Plus, we test their warranty claims and trade-in process with some eye-opening results. Are they worth those premium prices or should you look elsewhere for your retro gaming fix?

snippet.title: Ready or Not PS5 Review - A MUST PLAY Shooter
snippet.description:
A highly realistic, unerringly brutal tactical first-person shooter, that too with a good single-player component, is a tough call. Now try finding one inspired by one of the greatest of all time. the SWAT series, while standing out on its own.

Despite these heavy expectations and a somewhat repetitive campaign, Void Interactive's Ready or Not surprisingly steps up. As the leader of D Platoon, players embark on a harrowing journey through various missions, from robberies and busts to shootouts in deadly cabins rigged with traps. The gunplay is realistic, the tactics feel sound, and the presentation, especially the environments, is gritty and real.

Some iffy AI and a somewhat samey gameplay loop tend to bog things down, but thankfully, there's also co-op, where up to five players can team together for some chaotic fun. While Ready or Not won't revolutionize the genre, it does deserve some credit for going beyond simply paying tribute and delivering a worthwhile experience, even on consoles.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: A Semi-Truck CHANGED Their Lives… and Left Them in SHAMBLES
snippet.description:
Thank you to Earth Breeze for sponsoring this video! To save up to 40% off plus 4 free gifts go to https://earthbreeze.yt.link/VQK8tYR

After being hit by a semi-truck, her life was changed forever. The pain, the recovery, and the limitations that followed made even basic things—like yard work—impossible. Her family and neighbors stepped up to help where they could, but this property had become too much for anyone to manage. That’s when I got the call.

In this episode, we tackle one of the toughest cleanups I’ve ever seen—This isn’t just about overgrowth. It’s about resilience, compassion, and the healing power of helping one another.

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

"Zombies 4" introduces two warring groups of monsters, Daywalkers and Vampires, who inhabit two spectacular new worlds: east and west Rayburn, a world of perpetual day and a world of perpetual night. It’s up to Zed and Addison to help these two groups of sworn enemies find peace and common ground before their worlds suffer catastrophic consequences.

"Descendants/Zombies: Worlds Collide Tour" is a one-of-a-kind interactive live concert experience coming to arenas across North America in Summer 2025. The tour will feature Kylie Cantrall, Freya Skye, Malia Baker, Malachi Barton, Dara Reneé, Joshua Colley and Mekonnen Knife.  Kicking off in San Diego, CA on July 17, the arena tour will celebrate the chart-topping music from Disney’s “Descendants” and “Zombies” movie franchises, inspiring families, and fans of all ages to dance, sing, and engage with their favorite stars. You can click here for more information on dates, locations, and tickets - disneynow.com/descendantszombiestour

**In Loving Memory of Coach Tyler Wall**

It is with profound sadness that we share the unexpected passing of Coach Tyler Wall. Coach Wall was a remarkable individual whose kindness and genuine spirit touched all who knew him. His loss has left our hearts heavy with grief.

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் எதிர்பாராத மறைவுச் செய்தியை ஆழ்ந்த துக்கத்துடன் பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறோம். கோச் வால் ஒரு அற்புதமான மனிதர், அவரது கருணையும் உண்மையான மனப்பான்மையும் அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரையும் கவர்ந்தது. அவரது இழப்பு எங்கள் இதயங்களை துயரத்தால் கனக்கச் செய்துள்ளது.

இந்தத் துயரச் செய்தியைத் தொடர்ந்து, இந்த வீடியோவை வெளியிட வேண்டுமா என்று கோச் வால் குடும்பத்தினரை அணுகினோம். அவர்கள், தங்கள் ஞானத்தோடும் பெருந்தன்மையோடும், டைலர் இல்லாத நிலையிலும் அவரது நம்பிக்கை மற்றும் நேர்மறையான செய்தி மற்றவர்களைச் சென்றடைய வேண்டும் என்று விரும்பியிருப்பார் எனத் தெரிவித்தனர்.

இந்தக் கடினமான நேரத்தில் கோச் வால் அவர்களின் நினைவைப் போற்றுமாறும், அவரது குடும்பத்தினரின் தனிப்பட்ட உரிமையை மதிக்குமாறும் தாழ்மையுடன் கேட்டுக்கொள்கிறோம்.

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் இரக்கமும் ஊக்கமும் நிறைந்த மரபு, அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரின் இதயங்களிலும் நிலைத்திருக்கும்.

te.description:
కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ కు ప్రేమతో సమర్పణ

కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ అనుకోని రీతిలో ఈ లోకాన్ని విడిచిన విషాదవార్తను తెలియజేయడం చాలా బాధాకరం. కోచ్ వాల్ అందరి హృదయాలను తాకిన మానవత్వం, దయామయమైన వ్యక్తిత్వం కలిగిన అసాధారణ వ్యక్తి.

ఈ విషాదకర సంఘటన అనంతరం, ఈ వీడియోను పంచుకోవాలా వద్దా అనే విషయంలో కోచ్ వాల్ కుటుంబాన్ని సంప్రదించాం. వారి తెలివైన మరియు పరిపక్వమైన స్పందనలో, ""టైలర్ ఆశాభావం మరియు సానుకూలతను ప్రపంచానికి చేరవేయాలనే తన ఆకాంక్ష ఈ సమయంలో కూడా కొనసాగాలి"" అని చెప్పారు.

ఈ కష్ట సమయంలో, మీరు కోచ్ వాల్ యొక్క జ్ఞాపకాన్ని గౌరవించి, ఆయన కుటుంబానికి గౌరవంగా ప్రైవసీని కల్పించమని మనవి చేస్తున్నాము.

Koç Tyler Wall'un beklenmedik vefatını derin bir üzüntüyle paylaşıyoruz. Koç Wall, nezaketi ve samimi ruhuyla onu tanıyan herkesi etkileyen olağanüstü bir bireydi. Kaybı kalplerimizi kederle doldurdu.

hi.title: रिकॉर्ड तोड़ 6 विकेट | हाइलाइट्स | वेस्टइंडीज बनाम ऑस्ट्रेलिया | तीसरा टेस्ट दिन 3
hi.description:
किंग्स्टन के सबीना पार्क में वेस्टइंडीज और ऑस्ट्रेलिया के बीच खेले जा रहे तीसरे टेस्ट मैच के तीसरे दिन के हाइलाइट्स देखें।

snippet.title: $200 Cash If Randy and I Can Finish This 30" Team Pizza Challenge in Maine!
snippet.description:
Teaming up with @RandySantel to take on the 30" Gridiron Team Pizza Challenge at End Zone Pizza in Augusta, Maine! Teams of 2 have just 45 minutes to finish a 30" one-topping pizza in order to earn their meal for free, a groovy t-shirt, $200 cash, and a spot up on the wall of fame! Hungry diners may also attempt this solo and are granted a 90 minute time limit. Randy and I were a couple of silly gooses, however, and tried to be the first team to finish with several toppings (we each ordered specialty pizzas; I opted for the Hawaiian, Randy opted for the Philly Cheesesteak). Could we make history?!
***
RP Strength Code: KILOS
RP Diet App Link: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
RP Hypertrophy App Link: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
WEBSITE: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
About Me:
I'm a 5'2 former women's physique bodybuilder on a mission to sample delicious foods from around the world! I tackle restaurant challenges, sample new food menus, and explore the unique eats in various cities. To balance out the calorie intake of weekly food challenges, I continue to pursue my love of fitness through bodybuilding, running, and spinning. 

FAQ:
**How do you not get fat?** 
Please check out my "Daily Diet" Playlist Here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Why do you shake so much?**
I have a genetic condition known as "non-essential tremors". That in combination with nerves, being hungry with lowered blood sugar, and a deep and profound love affair with caffeine, makes for a rather jittery start to a challenge.

**Are you and Randy married?** 
No, not yet! We got engaged on December 1, 2024 though and are excited for the future!

pl.title: 200 dolarów w gotówce, jeśli Randy i ja ukończymy to wyzwanie drużynowe w Maine, polegające na kr...
pl.description:
Łączymy siły z @RandySantel, aby wziąć udział w 30" Gridiron Team Pizza Challenge w End Zone Pizza w Augusta, Maine! Dwuosobowe drużyny mają zaledwie 45 minut na zjedzenie 30" pizzy z jednym dodatkiem, aby zdobyć darmowy posiłek, odjazdową koszulkę, 200 dolarów w gotówce i miejsce na ścianie sław! Głodni goście mogą również spróbować tego solo i mają 90 minut na to. Randy i ja byliśmy jednak parą głupich gęsi i staraliśmy się być pierwszym zespołem, który skończy z kilkoma dodatkami (każdy z nas zamówił specjalną pizzę; ja wybrałem hawajską, Randy wybrał Philly Cheesesteak). Czy możemy zapisać się w historii?! ***
Kod siły RP: KILOS
Link do aplikacji RP Diet: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
Link do aplikacji RP Hypertrophy: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
STRONA INTERNETOWA: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
O mnie:
Jestem byłą kulturystką o wzroście 5'2, której misją jest próbowanie pysznych potraw z całego świata! Podejmuję wyzwania restauracyjne, próbuję nowych menu i odkrywam wyjątkowe potrawy w różnych miastach. Aby zrównoważyć spożycie kalorii w cotygodniowych wyzwaniach żywieniowych, nadal realizuję swoją miłość do fitnessu poprzez kulturystykę, bieganie i spinning.

FAQ:
**Jak nie tyć?** 
Sprawdź moją playlistę „Daily Diet” tutaj: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Dlaczego tak się trzęsiesz?**
Mam schorzenie genetyczne znane jako „drżenie niesamoistne”. To w połączeniu z nerwami, głodem i obniżonym poziomem cukru we krwi oraz głębokim i głębokim romansem z kofeiną sprawia, że ​​początek wyzwania jest dość nerwowy.

**Czy ty i Randy jesteście małżeństwem?** 
Nie, jeszcze nie! Zaręczyliśmy się 1 grudnia 2024 roku i jesteśmy podekscytowani przyszłością!

nl-NL.description:
Samen met @RandySantel ga ik de 30" Gridiron Team Pizza Challenge aan bij End Zone Pizza in Augusta, Maine! Teams van 2 hebben slechts 45 minuten om een ​​pizza van 30" met één topping op te eten en verdienen daarmee hun maaltijd gratis, een tof T-shirt, $200 cash en een plekje op de Wall of Fame! Hongerige gasten mogen dit ook alleen proberen en krijgen daarvoor een tijdslimiet van 90 minuten. Randy en ik waren echter een stelletje domme ganzen en probeerden als eerste team met meerdere toppings te finishen (we bestelden allebei speciale pizza's; ik koos voor de Hawaiiaanse, Randy koos voor de Philly Cheesesteak). Zouden we geschiedenis kunnen schrijven?! ***
RP Strength Code: KILO

***

***
Over mij:
Ik ben een 1,57 meter lange, voormalige bodybuilder met een missie om heerlijke gerechten van over de hele wereld te proeven! Ik ga restaurantuitdagingen aan, probeer nieuwe menu's en ontdek de unieke eetgelegenheden in verschillende steden. Om de calorie-inname van wekelijkse foodchallenges in balans te brengen, blijf ik mijn liefde voor fitness beoefenen door middel van bodybuilding, hardlopen en spinning.

Veelgestelde vragen:
**Hoe word je niet dik?**
Bekijk hier mijn afspeellijst "Dagelijks dieet": https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Waarom tril je zo veel?**
Ik heb een genetische aandoening die bekendstaat als "niet-essentiële tremoren". Dat, in combinatie met zenuwen, honger met een verlaagde bloedsuikerspiegel en een diepe en intense liefdesrelatie met cafeïne, zorgt voor een nogal nerveuze start van een uitdaging.

**Zijn jij en Randy getrouwd?**
Nee, nog niet! We zijn wel verloofd op 1 december 2024 en kijken uit naar de toekomst!

hi.title: यदि रैंडी और मैं मेन में 30" टीम पिज्जा चैलेंज पूरा कर सकें तो मुझे 200 डॉलर नकद मिलेंगे!
hi.description:
ऑगस्टा, मेन में एंड ज़ोन पिज़्ज़ा में 30" ग्रिडिरॉन टीम पिज़्ज़ा चैलेंज लेने के लिए @RandySantel के साथ मिलकर काम करना! 2 लोगों की टीमों के पास 30" वन-टॉपिंग पिज़्ज़ा खत्म करने के लिए सिर्फ़ 45 मिनट हैं, ताकि वे अपना भोजन मुफ़्त में कमा सकें, एक शानदार टी-शर्ट, $200 नकद और प्रसिद्धि की दीवार पर एक स्थान प्राप्त कर सकें! भूखे खाने वाले भी इसे अकेले करने का प्रयास कर सकते हैं और उन्हें 90 मिनट की समय सीमा दी जाती है। हालाँकि, रैंडी और मैं दो मूर्ख हंस थे, और हमने कई टॉपिंग के साथ खत्म करने वाली पहली टीम बनने की कोशिश की (हमने प्रत्येक ने विशेष पिज़्ज़ा ऑर्डर किया; मैंने हवाईयन चुना, रैंडी ने फिली चीज़स्टेक चुना)। क्या हम इतिहास बना सकते हैं?! ***
आरपी स्ट्रेंथ कोड: किलो
आरपी डाइट ऐप लिंक: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
आरपी हाइपरट्रॉफी ऐप लिंक: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
इंस्टाग्राम: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
वेबसाइट: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
मेरे बारे में:
मैं 5'2 की पूर्व महिला बॉडीबिल्डर हूँ, जो दुनिया भर के स्वादिष्ट खाद्य पदार्थों का नमूना लेने के मिशन पर हूँ! मैं रेस्तरां चुनौतियों का सामना करती हूँ, नए खाद्य मेनू का नमूना लेती हूँ, और विभिन्न शहरों में अनोखे खाने का पता लगाती हूँ। साप्ताहिक खाद्य चुनौतियों के कैलोरी सेवन को संतुलित करने के लिए, मैं बॉडीबिल्डिंग, रनिंग और स्पिनिंग के माध्यम से फिटनेस के प्रति अपने प्यार को आगे बढ़ाती रहती हूँ।

अक्सर पूछे जाने वाले प्रश्न:
**आप मोटे कैसे नहीं होते?**
कृपया मेरी "दैनिक आहार" प्लेलिस्ट यहाँ देखें: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**आप इतना क्यों काँपते हैं?**
मुझे एक आनुवंशिक बीमारी है जिसे "गैर-आवश्यक कंपन" के रूप में जाना जाता है। यह घबराहट, कम रक्त शर्करा के साथ भूख और कैफीन के साथ गहरे और गहन प्रेम संबंध के साथ मिलकर एक चुनौती की शुरुआत को थोड़ा बेचैन कर देता है।

**क्या आप और रैंडी विवाहित हैं?**
नहीं, अभी नहीं! हालाँकि हमारी सगाई 1 दिसंबर, 2024 को हुई है और हम भविष्य के लिए उत्साहित हैं!

fr-FR.description:
On fait équipe avec @RandySantel pour relever le Défi Pizza Gridiron de 76 cm chez End Zone Pizza à Augusta, dans le Maine ! Les équipes de 2 ont seulement 45 minutes pour terminer une pizza de 76 cm avec une seule garniture afin de gagner leur repas gratuit, un t-shirt tendance, 200 $ en espèces et une place au mur des célébrités ! Les plus affamés peuvent aussi tenter l’expérience en solo et ont un temps limité de 90 minutes. Randy et moi avons été un peu fous, et nous avons essayé d’être la première équipe à terminer avec plusieurs garnitures (nous avons chacun commandé des pizzas spéciales ; j’ai opté pour l’hawaïenne, Randy pour la Philly Cheesesteak). Allons-nous entrer dans l’histoire ?! ***
Code RP Force : KILOS

***

SITE WEB : https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
À propos de moi :
Je suis une ancienne culturiste de 1,58 m, dont la mission est de goûter aux délices culinaires du monde entier ! Je relève des défis gastronomiques, je teste de nouveaux menus et j'explore les saveurs uniques de différentes villes. Pour équilibrer mon apport calorique lors des défis alimentaires hebdomadaires, je continue à vivre ma passion pour le fitness grâce à la musculation, la course à pied et le spinning.

FAQ :
**Comment ne pas grossir ?**
Consultez ma playlist « Régime quotidien » ici : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Pourquoi tremblez-vous autant ?**
Je souffre d'une maladie génétique appelée « tremblements non essentiels ». Combinée à la nervosité, à la faim liée à une hypoglycémie et à une passion profonde pour la caféine, cette condition rend le début d'un défi plutôt stressant.

**Êtes-vous mariés avec Randy ?**
Non, pas encore ! Nous nous sommes fiancés le 1er décembre 2024 et nous sommes impatients de voir l'avenir !

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. snippet.title: We Tried the World’s Best River Cruise Safari
snippet.description:
Join us as we spend 4 days cruising up & down the Chobe River on a luxurious floating safari lodge with insane animal encounters!! Going to therapy is a sign of strength, not weakness. My sponsor BetterHelp makes therapy simple, with 10% off your first month to help you get started: https://betterhelp.com/kandn

Episode 964 | Filmed May 2025 | Chobe River, Botswana/Namibia border

Huge thanks to the entire team on the Zambezi Queen for having us!!! https://zqcollection.com/ It truly was a dream come true!

 Thank you https://www.youtube.com/@UCfddS1qHm5ux9O5oowCV80w for capturing the drone footage and letting us use it!

——————————————————

Want to save money on flights and hotels?! Check out our all new Daily Drop PRO 😍➡️  https://s.dailydrop.com/yt_kn 

✈️ @DailyDrop is our *FREE travel newsletter!* Get all the best travel news, tips, and tricks every weekday in your inbox by subscribing here ➡️
https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_sign-up

🌎 Our FREE Miles & Points 101 Course - https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_101

📸 Get behind the scenes content on our Instagram! @karaandnate
https://www.instagram.com/karaandnate/  

📧 Read our Sunday Summary email to know what goes on between videos -
https://karaandnate.com/sunday-summary/  

——————————————————

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s  

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW 

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

snippet.title: I ORDERED THE GIANT PHO CHALLENGE AT FLORIDA'S FAMOUS BLACK AND WHITE RESTAURANT! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Twenty Pho Hour in Orlando, Florida having a go at their $50 giant pho bowl challenge...

Noodle nuts get ONE HOUR in which to finish a huge bowl of pho, packed with brisket, beef shin, eggs, veggies, noodles and of course...lots of broth...

If you can finish it in the allotted time, the $50 meal isn't free, but you get some goodies (including a t-shirt) 'equal to the cost of the bowl'. You also get to write your name on one of the empty books decorating their wall...which is pretty cool...

ヌードルマニアの皆さんは、ブリスケット、牛すね肉、卵、野菜、麺、そしてもちろんたっぷりのスープが入った巨大なフォーボウルを1時間で完食しなければなりません…

hi.description:
इस सप्ताह के एपिसोड में हम फ्लोरिडा के ऑरलैंडो में ट्वेंटी फो ऑवर में हैं, जहाँ हम $50 के विशाल फो बाउल चैलेंज में भाग ले रहे हैं...

नूडल नट्स को एक घंटे का समय मिलता है, जिसमें वे एक बड़ा सा फो बाउल खत्म कर सकते हैं, जिसमें ब्रिस्केट, बीफ़ शिन, अंडे, सब्ज़ियाँ, नूडल्स और निश्चित रूप से...बहुत सारा शोरबा होता है...

यदि आप इसे आवंटित समय में खत्म कर देते हैं, तो $50 का भोजन मुफ़्त नहीं है, लेकिन आपको कुछ उपहार (जिसमें एक टी-शर्ट भी शामिल है) 'बाउल की कीमत के बराबर' मिलते हैं। आपको उनकी दीवार पर सजी खाली किताबों में से एक पर अपना नाम लिखने का मौका भी मिलता है...जो कि बहुत बढ़िया है...

इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों, विटैलिटी ब्लास्ट, काउंटी चैंपियनशिप, मेट्रो बैंक वन-डे कप और अन्य के वीडियो।

snippet.title: Clipse: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
Bobby Carter | July 11, 2025
After a 16-year hiatus and with no go-to band in place, Clipse's Tiny Desk took lots of time to piece together. At first, I didn't know exactly what they were looking for, in terms of sonics, but it clicked when I was told what they didn't want: no jazzy renditions of their music. They meant no disrespect to jazz at all, and if you follow the duo's music, it boils down to hard drums and even harder synths. Hybrid drummer Daru Jones, who played on last year's Tiny Desk for the LOX, was the first choice because of his unique ability to mix traditional and electronic drum sounds. He provided the authenticity needed for this set, and everything else fell into place.

The excitement for the Thornton brothers' return reached its apex instantly as someone in the crowd yelled "Oh my god!" at the opening note of "Virginia." There was no lull as the band coasted through "Keys Open Doors" and "Momma I'm So Sorry," from Clipse's most celebrated album, Hell Hath No Fury. I found so much to analyze witnessing the dichotomy between Pusha T and Malice up close. Malice is more collected in his movements, intensely scouring the room with his eyes while his brother is much more animated, even letting out a sinister laugh mid-set.

Recorded weeks ago, the two performed songs from their new album, Let God Sort Em Out, for the first time, including a chilling dedication to their deceased parents, "Birds Don't Sing." Before the tears from the crowd could dry, we got the moment we'd been waiting for in "Grindin'."

The first half of the year in hip-hop hasn't been the most exciting, so the timing of this reunion couldn't be better. Here's Clipse delivering its best live performance ever recorded and one of the hardest Tiny Desks of all time.

SET LIST
"Virginia"
"Keys Open Doors"
"Momma I'm So Sorry"
"Chains & Whips"
"Birds Don't Sing"
"Grindin'"

MUSICIANS
Pusha T: vocals
Malice: vocals
Briley Harris: keys
Darryl Woodson: keys
Yoo Q!: DJ, background vocals
Daru Jones: drums
Brittney Mills: background vocals
Tariq Ali: background vocals

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Bobby Carter
Director/Editor: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Mitra I. Arthur, Alanté Serene
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistant: Dhanika Pineda
Photographer: Michael Zamora
Copy Editor: Hazel Cills
Tiny Desk Team: Maia Stern, Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
